text: Karakulevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Ariyevsky Selsoviet, Duvansky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 357 as of 2010. There are 6 streets. == Geography == It is located 5 km from Mesyagutovo, 6 km from Ariyevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Duvansky District
title: Karakulevo
